N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 2 ยง 500.2 - Date of deposit

State Regulations

Contributions by the State and its political subdivisions
will be considered to be deposited on the date that such contribution is
received by the agency in Albany, New York. Notes
